    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive home in this wonderful, well-maintained vehicle! It's in good condition and offers a consistently smooth and reliable ride that you can count on. While it shows a few minor signs of past adventures, it has been cared for beautifully and is ready for many more miles of memories. This is a fantastic opportunity to own a quality car that balances performance and value perfectly!",
